Classes in org.epochx.tools.random that implement RandomNumberGenerator
 class JavaRandom
          Provides a mechanism for using Java's random number generation through EpochX's supported RandomNumberGenerator interface.
 class MersenneTwisterFast
          The Mersenne twister is a pseudorandom number generator developed in 1997 by Makoto Matsumoto and Takuji Nishimura that is based on a matrix linear recurrence over a finite binary field F2.
